description: Request for Screening Opinion in accordance with Regulation 6 of the Town and Country Planning (Environmental Impact Assessment) Regulations 2017 (as amended) for the construction of a part two, part three and part four-storey 6.5 Form Entry secondary school (1,330 pupils and 10,024 sq. m. GIA floorspace); installation of multi-use game areas; construction of a vehicle access from Park View Road pedestrian access from the North Circular Road; and associated car parking and hardstanding; boundary treatment works; refuse and cycle parking storage
